00:56:07,067 --> 00:56:08,862
Tidak ada nama pengirim lagi.

545
00:56:08,862 --> 00:56:10,674
Haruskah kita telepon
Pihak Pengawasan Internal?

546
00:56:12,189 --> 00:56:13,496
<i>[Manajer Saman E & C, Park Dong Hoon]</i>

547
00:56:14,093 --> 00:56:15,678
Jangan.

